<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="興福" xml:id="gsz0885b13shiZhiJiang"><lb
ed="T" n="0885b13"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0885b13"/><head><date from-iso="+0951-02-18" key="j20684542071729" to-iso="+0960-02-06">周</date><placeName key="PL000000049328">宋州廣壽院</placeName><persName key="A013797">智江</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0885b14"/><persName key="A013797">釋智江</persName>，俗姓<name>單</name>，<placeName key="PL000000003434"><placeName>幽州</placeName><placeName>三河</placeName><placeName>南管</placeName></placeName>人也。本富族<lb
ed="T" n="0885b15"/>遊俠之子，雖乘竹馬，厭迴火宅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1598"/>之門；乍玩<lb
ed="T" n="0885b16"/>沙堆，好作浮圖之制。略聞<placeName key="PL000000048207">竺乾</placeName>之教，必淡<lb
ed="T" n="0885b17"/>慮凝情，若<placeName key="PL000000028611">瀟湘</placeName>之逢故人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2281"/>也。<date from-iso="+0897-02-10" key="j20487242049077" to-iso="+0898-01-29"><name>唐</name><name>乾寧</name>四載</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0885b18"/>始年十五，詣<placeName key="PL000000000758"><placeName>盤山</placeName><placeName>感化寺</placeName></placeName>遂成息慈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g964"/>，息慈業<lb
ed="T" n="0885b19"/>備。<date from-iso="+0903-02-06" key="j20509102051263" to-iso="+0904-01-25"><name>天復</name>三祀</date>，往<placeName key="PL000000005422"><placeName>五臺山</placeName><placeName>梨園寺</placeName></placeName>納木叉法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1202"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0885b20"/><anchor xml:id="beg0885sgsz9"/>自<anchor xml:id="end0885sgsz9"/>此<anchor xml:id="beg0885001"/>擔<anchor xml:id="end0885001"/>簦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g76"/>請業，擇木<ptr type="glossary" target="#g528"/>依師，《淨名》<ptr target="#n1177"/>、《上生》<ptr target="#n772"/>二典<lb
ed="T" n="0885b21"/>精練，渙然氷釋，心未屬厭<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2282"/>。<date from-iso="+0921-02-16" key="j20574952057848" to-iso="+0922-02-04"><name>梁</name><name>龍德</name>元年</date>於<placeName key="PL000000025534"><placeName>商<lb
ed="T" n="0885b22"/>丘</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0885sgsz11"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>請</sic><corr>講</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0885sgsz11"/>《名數》一支<ptr target="#n1275"/>，所謂精義入神<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2284"/>，散則<lb
ed="T" n="0885b23"/>繁衍<ptr target="#n3450"/>，因著《瑞應鈔》八卷，達者傳之。生徒影<lb
ed="T" n="0885b24"/>附，繕寫夥多。<date from-iso="+0923-01-25" key="j20582032058586" to-iso="+0924-02-12"><name>後唐</name><name>同光</name>元年</date>，在<persName key="A013798">微子</persName>之墟住<lb
ed="T" n="0885b25"/>院<ptr target="#n805"/>，締搆堂宇，輪奐可觀。復塑<persName key="A001428">慈氏</persName>、<persName key="A002799">釋迦</persName>二<lb
ed="T" n="0885b26"/>尊、十六羅漢像，咸加<anchor xml:id="beg0885002"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>績</sic><corr>繢</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0885002"/>彩，克肖聖儀。善務<lb
ed="T" n="0885b27"/>方辦，俄遘沈痾，以<date from-iso="+0958-07-24" key="j20711672071196" to-iso="+0958-08-22"><name>周</name><name>顯德</name>五年孟秋</date>順終，<lb
ed="T" n="0885b28"/>享齡七十四。當屬纊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2283"/>時，滿院天人雜沓，若迎<lb
ed="T" n="0885b29"/>導之狀，疇昔誓生<placeName key="PL000000055446">覩史</placeName>之昭應也。吏部員<pb ed="T" n="0885c" xml:id="T50.2061.0885c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0885c01"/>外郎<persName key="A013788">李鉉</persName>著〈塔銘〉云。</p><p><lb
ed="T" n="0885c02"/>系曰：前人立義，皆按教文，豈得好惡隨情，<lb
ed="T" n="0885c03"/>是非任見？已行前轍，不覆後車，胡不謹而<lb
ed="T" n="0885c04"/>循之？通曰：「夫創著述者有四焉：一前說極<lb
ed="T" n="0885c05"/>非，於文茫昧；一僻見謬解，領悟自乖；一樂<lb
ed="T" n="0885c06"/>繁嫌略；一好直怪迂。有一於此，無不<lb
ed="T" n="0885c07"/>著述也。<persName key="A013797">江<roleName>公</roleName></persName>《瑞應鈔》未經披覽，聞諸道路，<lb
ed="T" n="0885c08"/>言亦濟時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2285"/>。須<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2286"/>苟不濟用而變革古德義章，<lb
ed="T" n="0885c09"/>則何異以『舊防無所用而壞之者，必有水<lb
ed="T" n="0885c10"/>敗』也。<ptr target="#n3451"/>」</p>
